# Cline Rules for pega-datascientist-tools

**Read and follow all guidelines in CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md**

These files contain comprehensive project conventions, code quality standards, and critical rules including:

- **Open Source Confidentiality** (CRITICAL) - Never include customer names or data
- Git workflow rules
- Code quality standards
- Python type hints and conventions
- Testing requirements
- Streamlit app patterns
- Tool preferences (uv, Polars)

The CLAUDE.md file is specifically designed for AI assistant context and contains all rules that must be followed when working on this codebase.
